Private Sub Detail_Format(Cancel As Integer, FormatCount As Integer)
  ' Check for student 2 and 3
  On Error GoTo SubError
  Dim frs As Recordset
  Dim criteria As String
  criteria = "SELECT [LNAME] & ', ' & [FNAME] & ' ' & [MI] AS Name, " & _
  "ExhibitStudents.F_ORD, ExhibitStudents.EXN FROM " & _
  "(Persons RIGHT JOIN Students ON (Persons.PID = Students.PID) AND " & _
  "(Persons.PID = Students.PID) AND (Persons.PID = Students.PID)) " & _
  "RIGHT JOIN (ExhibitData RIGHT JOIN ExhibitStudents ON ExhibitData.EXN " & _
  "= ExhibitStudents.EXN) ON Students.STID = ExhibitStudents.STID " & _
  "WHERE (((ExhibitStudents.F_ORD) > 1)) " & _
  "ORDER BY ExhibitStudents.EXN;"
  Me.tbStud2 = ""
  Me.tbStud3 = ""
  Set frs = CurrentDb().OpenRecordset(criteria, dbOpenDynaset)
  With frs
    .FindFirst "ExhibitStudents.EXN = " & Me.EXN
    If Not .NoMatch Then
      Do While Not .EOF And Not .NoMatch
        If Me.EXN = !EXN Then
          If !F_ORD = 2 Then
            Me.tbStud2 = !Name
          End If
          If !F_ORD = 3 Then
            
            Me.tbStud3 = !Name
          End If
         .FindNext "ExhibitStudents.EXN = " & Me.EXN
       End If
      Loop
    End If
    .Close
  End With
  Exit Sub
SubError:
  MsgBox Err.Description
End Sub
